---
// Por que escolher a Prado - Seção moderna com glassmorphism
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-16 bg-[#121212] z-1 overflow-visible">
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 50px 50px;"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Floating Elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="floating-element absolute top-20 left-10 w-2 h-2 bg-[#00B050] rounded-full opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="floating-element absolute top-40 right-20 w-1 h-1 bg-blue-400 rounded-full opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="floating-element absolute bottom-40 left-20 w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-400 rounded-full opacity-35"></div>
    <div class="floating-element absolute bottom-20 right-40 w-1 h-1 bg-orange-400 rounded-full opacity-25"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Header da Seção -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3 md:mb-8 leading-tight">
        <span class="text-white">
          Por que escolher a
        </span>
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Prado Soluções Digitais?
        </span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-white/70 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed px-2">
        Somos uma empresa jovem e inovadora, focada em entregar soluções digitais que realmente fazem a diferença no seu negócio.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-10 md:mb-24">
      <!-- Diferencial 1: Inovação -->
      <div class="group">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-[#00B050]/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 p-4 md:p-8 hover:scale-[1.02]">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-[#00B050]/20 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#00B050] group-hover:bg-[#00B050]/30 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-8 md:h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1 md:mb-3">Foco na Inovação</h3>
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Utilizamos as tecnologias mais atuais do mercado para criar soluções modernas e eficientes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Diferencial 2: Atendimento -->
      <div class="group">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 p-4 md:p-8 hover:scale-[1.02]">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 group-hover:bg-blue-500/30 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-8 md:h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1 md:mb-3">Atendimento Personalizado</h3>
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Cada cliente é único. Oferecemos atenção personalizada e soluções sob medida para suas necessidades.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Diferencial 3: Crescimento -->
      <div class="group">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 p-4 md:p-8 hover:scale-[1.02]">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 group-hover:bg-purple-500/30 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-8 md:h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1 md:mb-3">Crescimento Conjunto</h3>
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Seu sucesso é o nosso sucesso. Criamos parcerias duradouras e acompanhamos seu crescimento.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Diferencial 4: Qualidade -->
      <div class="group">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 p-4 md:p-8 hover:scale-[1.02]">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange-500/20 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-400 group-hover:bg-orange-500/30 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-8 md:h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1 md:mb-3">Excelência Técnica</h3>
              <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Código limpo, eficiente e bem documentado. Seguimos as melhores práticas de desenvolvimento.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Nossa Missão -->
    <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-24">
      <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-5 md:p-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left gap-3 md:gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-20 md:h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00B050]/20 to-blue-500/20 rounded-xl text-[#00B050] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto md:mx-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 md:w-10 md:h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 00-2.91-.09zM12 15l-3-3a22 22 0 012-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0122 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 01-4 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2 md:mb-1">Nossa Missão</h3>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              Democratizar o acesso à tecnologia de qualidade, criando soluções digitais acessíveis e eficientes que impulsionam o crescimento.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 md:gap-6">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="group flex flex-col">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-[#00B050]/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 p-3 md:p-6 hover:scale-[1.02] h-full flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-[#00B050]/20 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#00B050] group-hover:bg-[#00B050]/30 transition-colors duration-300 mb-2 md:mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-6 md:h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm md:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1 md:mb-2">Agilidade</h3>
          <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Desenvolvimento rápido e eficiente</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="group flex flex-col">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 p-3 md:p-6 hover:scale-[1.02] h-full flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 group-hover:bg-blue-500/30 transition-colors duration-300 mb-2 md:mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-6 md:h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm md:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1 md:mb-2">Design Moderno</h3>
          <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Interfaces intuitivas e ágeis</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="group flex flex-col">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 p-3 md:p-6 hover:scale-[1.02] h-full flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 group-hover:bg-purple-500/30 transition-colors duration-300 mb-2 md:mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-6 md:h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm md:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1 md:mb-2">Alta Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Otimização para velocidade</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="group flex flex-col">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/10 p-3 md:p-6 hover:scale-[1.02] h-full flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-orange-500/20 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-400 group-hover:bg-orange-500/30 transition-colors duration-300 mb-2 md:mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-6 md:h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192L5.636 18.364M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm md:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1 md:mb-2">Suporte Completo</h3>
          <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">Acompanhamento contínuo</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .floating-element {
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .floating-element:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: -2s;
  }

  .floating-element:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: -4s;
  }

  .floating-element:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: -6s;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-20px);
    }
  }
</style> 